text: Five little crayons jumping on the bed
One fell off and bumped its head
Mummy called the doctor and the doctor said,
"No more crayons jumping on the bed!"
Four little crayons jumping on the bed
One fell off and bumped its head
Mummy called the doctor and the doctor said,
"No more crayons jumping on the bed!"
Three little crayons jumping on the bed
One fell off and bumped its head
Mummy called the doctor and the doctor said,
"No more crayons jumping on the bed!"
Two little crayons jumping on the bed
One fell off and bumped its head
Mummy called the doctor and the doctor said,
"No more crayons jumping on the bed!"
One little crayons jumping on the bed
It fell off and bumped its head
Mummy called the doctor and the doctor said,
"Put those crayons right to bed!"
